				<p>Ultimately, I want my site to advertise my web development business platform in addition to my previous design career. I want to maintain a high- end aesthetic suitable for design minded clients who might (or might not) be more visually inclined, have a design/ innovation to advertise, an image/ video gallery focus, or a product to sell. In short, encapsulating my goals with "Design & Development" services. </p>
